SA: Valid ways in VHDL to specify 8-bit std_logic_vectors

Given the VHDL process below. Assume the value of signal a is '0'. What is the value of signal f?

process(ALL) begin
    f <= "1111";
    if a = '1' then
        f <= "1010";
    end if;
end process;
